---
title: Cherry, Thyme & Balsamic-Glazed Pork with Roast Veggie Toss & Toasted Almonds
description: Oh, happy days! With a heavenly combination of colourful roasted veggies tossed among salad leaves, and a sticky-sweet cherry
glaze enveloping the pork, this is a modern and delicious union that will be happily devoured by all.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cherry-balsamic-glazed-pork-a7a3d400.jpg
